info.title: Hotels 3.0 application
info.description:
Interbook is the hotel central reservation system, it is used mostly in the hotel and resort industry. It stores the information of various hotels in an organized manner in a centralized inventory management repository. Hotel Extranet helps the travel companies in reaching the global distribution system or GDS along with the internal distribution channel.
Hotel Extranet facilitates the functioning of agencies, travel companies, hospitality Vendors to manage online booking quickly and efficiently. Hotel industry is very dynamic in nature, in order to be ahead of the competition, you as a travel business should have technical know-how and have a hotel extranet in place. Hotel Extranet helps you connect with global clients by providing them with unique search and booking functionality. It also helps you create and promote your private inventory, create your own hotel listings, compete with existing hotels from GDS or Vendors with your private inventory
